          <h3 class="title"><a href="/call-for-submissions-blogging-textbook#comment-5131" class="active">I&#039;d be wary of Allyn and Bacon</a></h3> 
        <img src="http://kairosnews.org/sites/all/themes/blogbuzz/images/comment_arrow.png" class="comment_arrow" />
    <p>Barclay,</p>
<p>This is great news and I wish you luck with the project. However, I'd be a little cautious about their promises. They have the habit of reneging on contracts or changing their terms at the last minute, and I am not speaking only from personal experience. Will this be a printed work or an online one?</p>
<p>Pavel.</p>
     
